data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom/2 Bathroom home on a half acre located just minutes from Lake City. With 1,400 sq ft, there's plenty of space for the whole family! This home also offers a 4th room that could be used as the perfect office space, home gym, or den... the possibilities are endless! Entertaining just got easier with a fenced back yard which includes a brand new professionally installed above ground pool with a deck, concrete slab for grilling and metal carport. Home is zoned for Columbia County School District and Belmont Academy. Located 10 minutes from the heart of Lake City and I75. Don't miss this awesome opportunity for convenience and comfort at a great price!
